commitResults.messageBody:
Rename CommandParser as CommandProcessor and add a Map<String, Class<? extends Command>> method variant for O(1)-time command lookup instead of O(n)-time switch-case parsing.
Rename processCommand() to processCommandByMap() and update call sites accordingly.
Update SteadyLah to separate cache loading and saving for tasks and system state (loadFromCache() → loadTasksFromCache(), saveToCache() → saveTasksToCache()).
Comment out erstwhile-redundant continue statements. in DateTime class more meaningfully.

Impacts
Reduce command processing overhead, improving scalability.
Enhance maintainability by decoupling cache persistence responsibilities.
Bundle project's custom runtime exceptions.
Ensure better and more readable error handling in datetime parsing.
